{"tid":640741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"未補地價居屋轉名比子女","createTime":"2018-04-24T13:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T03:28:20.000Z","uid":39784,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d767bc934db0a1865b7b01dde6477a17260a2b64","tid":640741,"uid":39784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:26:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿媽想將名下唯一既未補地價居屋物業轉比個仔<br />\n想問下洗唔洗補地價或者比咩印花稅？<br />\n個仔係乜春都無既廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個單位連埋老豆一家三口住左廿幾年<br />\n房委會唔會唔批轉名架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n已知轉名係要有特別原因 可唔可以老豆老母搬出去 跟住轉名比個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>(C) 因結婚搬走與配偶同住而將業權轉給其他家庭成員；</strong>"},{"pid":"41797352a53c9f20e402dee743b4d2e6382df9e6","tid":640741,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:28:32.000Z","msg":"唔得除非死左"},{"pid":"6b67b5d69cc1960a9c0cfa23ff1c3e0e1038a7c8","tid":640741,"uid":101390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:42:17.000Z","msg":"咁我又想問假設老豆老母離婚<br />\n仲有冇機會轉名比仔女？"},{"pid":"a8c25d1de3a13ae7a9dcbb7d8afef388a74870f0","tid":640741,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:48:17.000Z","msg":"死左可以免費轉"},{"pid":"c9ab26d2fb36658611edfb7729645acb7ff6aa8b","tid":640741,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:49:11.000Z","msg":"除非夠65歲或者有危疾啦，否則都唔俾轉名。<br />\n<br />\n或者你補地價買左佢囉。"},{"pid":"33ef9f285d9e17bff61747591515ba8ba4ac9450","tid":640741,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:19:39.000Z","msg":"轉名黎做乜 遲早都係你既 <br />\n你又繼續擁有首置呢個機會"},{"pid":"f495eade6516f78cca48bd9512c0d63364b5bd0e","tid":640741,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33ef9f285d9e17bff61747591515ba8ba4ac9450","tid":64074